{"tid":428402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：泛民做得唔好就斬頭！","createTime":"2017-10-08T04:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T15:06:16.000Z","uid":136994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de1a927b02305738ae811ddab7a4a5e06fb2153b","tid":428402,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171008/s00001/1507434142727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171008%2Fs00001%2F1507434142727&d=4XQIVCbeeCMwHoKAx8ePbUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c26b82c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171008%2Fs00001%2F1507434142727&h=8c1fd8c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171008/s00001/1507434142727</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會將於周三（11日）正式復會，建制派擬修改《議事規則》及《財委會會議程序》抗衡泛民主派拉布。建制派議員何君堯認為，如果成功修改議事規則，可讓泛民知道「頭上有把刀」，「稍為做得唔好就『斬頭』」。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯昨晚於facebook直播中指，要與民主派交手，搞好議事規則，建制派就必須把握時間及團結，「如果改到大部分議事規則內容，加重行為不檢刑罰，等佢哋知道『頭上有把刀』，稍為做得唔好就『斬頭』，呢個必須要做到」。<br />\n<br />\n至於立法會譴責何君堯「殺無赦」言論動議，何君堯批評做法「無經大腦」，他會沉着應戰，星期三前亦會向民主派發信，問「究竟攻擊何君堯是借題發揮，還是支持港獨，還是真正想要有一個撥亂反正，糾正社會風氣，（因）何君堯真係錯得好犀利，所以要將佢要處理，讓社會重新有一個清新風格？」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯指，如果是後者，他會思考如何配合，但若只是想「攞彩」，就會徒勞無功。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯亦感謝建制派於會上「鼎力支持」他，「君堯會銘記心中的！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何君堯真係好鬼暴力<br />\n成日唔係殺就係斬頭<br />\n荼毒兒童心靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9211d052a4905a91774982720abeccb34220f70","tid":428402,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2693969ff6e288603db23a1bf621fd9f2c3ebbd6","tid":428402,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:43:26.000Z","msg":"知道自己死到臨頭，開始發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa1359f85a9e8ddd99bc672b153cd54b3a722b2","tid":428402,"uid":58046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"343d5ccb11e15cfa1c3d3c8803b40dee4f364a04","tid":428402,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:26:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3aecc5acd2df259fe27bac7724b0eb23419ae9f6","tid":428402,"uid":4874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T10:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4417e87d390e561785c6e009e15363416a9e5605","tid":428402,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T15:06:16.000Z","msg":"圍頭爛鬼係咁上下"}]}